{"tid":2019104,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"17歲青年在寓所墮樓身亡！！！","createTime":"2020-05-16T05:05:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-16T05:18:36.000Z","uid":229185,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"fb4d6615626e75dcd0abb46269f8be28ca73bde2","tid":2019104,"uid":229185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T05:05:00.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】大角嘴君滙港一名生活不如意，上月曾危坐窗外簷篷12小時懷疑企圖跳樓的17歲青年，昨晚深夜終踏上不歸路，在寓所墮樓身亡。<br />\n<br />\n現場為深旺道8號。警方昨晚11時14分接獲事主的19歲姊姊報案，指懷疑胞弟從高處墮下。警員接報到場，發現事主倒臥君滙港1座平台，昏迷被送往廣華醫院治理，其後被證實死亡。警方於現場沒有檢獲遺書，初步調查相信從一單位墮下，事件沒有可疑，死因有待驗屍後確定。<br />\n<br />\n警方4月11日下午曾接獲事主的母親報案，指兒子反鎖屋內。警員接報到場後，在窗外的青年於簷篷闊約1呎的石壆上不斷改變姿勢，時坐時臥，事件擾攘12小時，當時16歲的青年於翌日凌晨被勸服返回屋內。事件起因疑與青年廢寢忘餐打機有關。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/%E4%B8%8A%E6%9C%88%E5%8D%B1%E5%9D%90%E7%AA%97%E5%A4%9612%E5%B0%8F%E6%99%82%E4%BC%81%E8%B7%B3-%E5%90%9B%E6%BB%99%E6%B8%AF17%E6%AD%B2%E4%BB%94%E5%A2%AE%E6%96%83-001100242.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%25E4%25B8%258A%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%258D%25B1%25E5%259D%2590%25E7%25AA%2597%25E5%25A4%259612%25E5%25B0%258F%25E6%2599%2582%25E4%25BC%2581%25E8%25B7%25B3-%25E5%2590%259B%25E6%25BB%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF17%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E4%25BB%2594%25E5%25A2%25AE%25E6%2596%2583-001100242.html&d=IqGrl%2FmL2I6%2Fp6gKwmVM%2BfsPRfgRtgRFNgQ5kFpanIU%3D&h=1dbf2762\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/%E4%B8%8A%E6%9C%88%E5%8D%B1%E5%9D%90%E7%AA%97%E5%A4%9612%E5%B0%8F%E6%99%82%E4%BC%81%E8%B7%B3-%E5%90%9B%E6%BB%99%E6%B8%AF17%E6%AD%B2%E4%BB%94%E5%A2%AE%E6%96%83-001100242.html</a>"},{"pid":"ac08292bc834924ec4e8e8bb39acde0cae8d9005","tid":2019104,"uid":229185,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T05:07:03.000Z","msg":"點解會咁架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"563303f74e7a13ef